		<div>The only concern I have about using magic nukes is that so many mobs seem to be more resistant to it, supposedly to make it more difficult to slow them.  Tash and Malo should knock it down a bit but I (anecdotaly) seem to recall a lot more difficulty landing magic nukes even after that.  Most of my experiences with this were in Anguish, where I have most of my high end experience, but we do that at most once a week now.<br />
<br />
Having said that, if it works for you at your level, it should work for me.  Just curious where you guys raid mostly, Kela?  We haven't been able to beat Queen Sendaii more than once because now that we have the encounter beaten the freaking zone crashes in wave 3 EVERY TIME. . .otherwise, we would be in DPoB by now (which I understand crashes all the time as well /sigh)</div>
